n. Issue #30.~~ Pushed for future release.\r\n* ~~ \u2610 Laser reflecting the ocean. Issue #29. Pushed for future release.~~\r\n* ~~ \u2610 Acoustic beacons. Issue #26. Pushed for future release.~~\r\n* ~~ \u2610 Wave physical and rendering synchronization. See issue #23. Pushed for future release.~~\r\n* \u2611 Create a .Deb package. Issue #50.\r\n* \u2610 Tutorial review.\r\n\r\nOptional:\r\n\r\n* \u2610 Better buoyancy model based on multiple simple shapes.\r\n* \u2610 Create nice sensor meshes.\r\n* \u2610 Create mesh to mount the lateral thruster (if present).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p><strong>Deadline: October 15th.</strong></p>\n<p>Required:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u2611 Task draft.</li>\n<li>\u2610 Docker maintenance and improvements.<ul>\n<li>\u2611 Build images automatically. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/36/trigger-the-creation-of-new-images\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Trigger the creation of new images automatically\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#36</s></a> and <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/55/set-uid-and-gid-of-container-user-at\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Set UID and GID of container user at runtime\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#55</s></a></li>\n<li>\u2610 Tutorial update. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/37/update-sand_island_basic-tutorial-for\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Update Sand_Island_Basic tutorial for compatibility with Docker-based install path\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#37</s></a>. </li>\n<li><del> \u2610 Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/45/docker-image-non-nvidia-image-seg-faults\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Docker Image: Non-NVIDIA image seg faults on NVIDIA system\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#45</s></a>. Pushed for future release. </del></li>\n<li>\u2611 Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/47/buildbash-can-pass-illegal-input-to-docker\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"build.bash can pass illegal input to Docker tag\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#47</s></a>. </li>\n<li>\u2611 Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/53/update-docker-image-to-use-new-ros-package\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Update Docker Image to use new ROS package names\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#53</s></a>. Update Docker image in repo. </li>\n<li>\u2610 Update Docker-based tutorials to use new package names.     </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><del> \u2610 Refine sensor configuration. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/30/refine-default-sensor-configurations\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Refine default sensor configurations\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#30</s></a>.</del> Pushed for future release.</li>\n<li><del> \u2610 Laser reflecting the ocean. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/29/the-ocean-reflects-the-laser-beams\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"The ocean reflects the laser beams\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#29</s></a>. Pushed for future release.</del></li>\n<li><del> \u2610 Acoustic beacons. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/26/acoustic-beacon-range-and-bearing\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Acoustic beacon - range and bearing\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#26</s></a>. Pushed for future release.</del></li>\n<li><del> \u2610 Wave physical and rendering synchronization. See issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/23/coordinate-the-physics-and-visualization\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Coordinate the physics and visualization of the wave field\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#23</s></a>. Pushed for future release.</del></li>\n<li>\u2611 Create a .Deb package. Issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/vrx/issues/50/add-all-vmrc-ros-packages-to-the-ros\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Add all VMRC ROS packages to the ROS package repository\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#50</s></a>.</li>\n<li>\u2610 Tutorial review.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Optional:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u2610 Better buoyancy model based on multiple simple shapes.</li>\n<li>\u2610 Create nice sensor meshes.</li>\n<li>\u2610 Create mesh to mount the lateral thruster (if present).</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "